{
    "typeName": "TF::NSXT::PolicyDhcpServer",
    "description": "This resource provides a method for the management of a DHCP Server configurations.\n\nThis resource is applicable to NSX Global Manager, and NSX Policy Manager.\n\nThis resource is supported with NSX 3.0.0 onwards.",
